00:01:19.568 --> 00:01:25.305
To the outside world, Anna Chapman was a successful internet entrepreneur.

00:01:26.055 --> 00:01:34.065
She arrived in New York in 2006 at the age of 24 with little more than a dream, and a few years

00:01:34.065 --> 00:01:40.475
later, she was running an apparently successful online estate agency, employing 50 people.

00:01:41.775 --> 00:01:48.775
But in the summer of 2010, she got an unexpected knock on her door.

