She was arrested for being part of a Russian spy ring, sent by Moscow to the

00:01:58.415 --> 00:02:05.695
United States to live and exist, on the face of it, regular, mundane, normal lives.

00:02:07.175 --> 00:02:13.025
Chapman, or Kushchenko, as she was before she married and took her husband’s name, was

