in forests with their telescopes; their instructions were to melt into American

00:02:48.275 --> 00:02:53.675
society so that they would appear just like any, good, law-abiding citizen.

00:02:55.125 --> 00:03:00.355
Their ultimate goal was to get information that might be useful to the Russian

00:03:00.355 --> 00:03:06.425
state, information about US foreign policy, US policy towards Russia, military

00:03:06.425 --> 00:03:12.335
secrets and so on, and the idea was that they would make friends and business

00:03:12.335 --> 00:03:16.799
contacts with people who could provide them with information that might be useful.

