As a reminder, this was part of a three-part mini-series

00:20:30.945 --> 00:20:33.555
on the loose theme of mystery and the unknown.

00:20:34.040 --> 00:20:37.580
Part one was on secret societies, and next we are going to

00:20:37.590 --> 00:20:41.700
take a look at the very mysterious world of lost civilisations.

